articles.title: Baseball fan goes viral after proposal goes VERY wrong at Dodgers game - Daily Mail
articles.description: A romantic Los Angeles Dodgers fan got more than he bargained for when he tried to propose to his girlfriend on the field - only to be slammed by a security guard as he got down on one knee.
